OpenEXR-Handling
================

Author: 	Andrew Chalmers

Basic I/O for OpenEXR images. 

Usage:
make clean
make
./bin/exrExample [filename.exr]

Output:
original_float1.exr 
original_float2.exr 
original_half.exr 
original_rgba.exr 

Example Usage:
./bin/exrExample images/example.exr

TODO:
